name: Fearless.
description: Taken while on assignment with a group of pro-bono NYC surgeons in Dehradun, India in 2011. She was moments away from being anesthetized and operated on (to remove massive burn scarring around her neck and chest). She didnâ€™t speak a word of english, but listened intently to every word said. She knew what was about to happen, but showed no signs of nervousness or fear. Her name is Anjeli.
